column5: Good morning love! Hope you have a productive Monday.
Morning! Gonna need a gallon of coffee for this lab session.
Lunch? I'm starving.
Can't babe. Stuck in the library with a group project.
I'm coming over tonight. Want me to pick up Thai food?
Sounds perfect. See you at 8.
Did you leave your charger at my place?
Yeah! Keep it safe. I'll grab it later.
You've been so quiet today. Everything okay?
Just tired. This CS project is draining me.
Checking in! Miss you.
Miss you too! Almost done with work.
Why are you still on Messenger? I saw your active status.
It's for the project group. They don't use WhatsApp for some reason.
Don't forget our dinner date tomorrow! Pre-Valentine's.
I won't! Reserved the table already.
Happy Valentine's Day Rahul!
Happy Valentine's Day! Can't wait for tonight.
Thank you for the necklace. I love it so much.
You deserve it. Glad you liked it.
Are you coming to the library? I'm here.
Gonna be late. Group meeting ran over.
My roommate said she saw you leaving the building at 2 AM?
What? No I was in the computer lab all night. She must be mistaken.
Post this photo on your IG? We look so cute.
Sure! Doing it now.
Morning sunshine. Have a great week.
You too! Lots of work this week.
Remember Saturday is my cousin's wedding. I told you last week.
Wait... wedding? I just bought tickets for that concert on Saturday!
Rahul... I told you about this dinner Tuesday night.
You definitely didn't. The tickets are non-refundable Anjali.
So you're choosing a concert over my family?
It's not about that. It's about communication.
I'm heading to the venue. My parents are asking where you are.
I'm at the concert. We'll talk tomorrow.
I hope the concert was worth the fight.
Don't do this right now. I'm with family today.
I'm staying at my mom's tonight. I need some space.
Space? For what?
Your phone kept buzzing while you were in the shower yesterday.
So? It's just project notifications.
Why did you delete the Messenger app?
It was taking up too much storage. Why are you interrogating me?
I feel like I don't even know what's going on with you anymore.
Are we still going to the movie Friday?
Of course. Let's not fight.
Where are you? You said you'd be here by 7.
Car trouble. On my way now.
My parents want to meet for lunch to discuss the 'marriage' talk.
Marriage? Isn't it a bit early for that?
You're being very cold lately.
I'm going to my parents' for the weekend. Do you want to come?
Can't. Lots of catch-up work. Enjoy the break.
I miss you. Can we talk?
Morning. Yeah
column6: I'll call you in a bit.
